data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ASSUMABLE 4.6% VA LOAN AVAILABLE FOR ALL VA BUYERS!! COME SEE IT TODAY. This 3 car garage BEAUTIFUL HOME built in 2020 is located in one of the most popular gated Lennar Homes communities in central Florida - Arden Park! There are brand new homes still being built in this community, but the waiting list for a new build is long. Take advantage of this gorgeous home while you can! This 3 bedroom/2 bath home is like new and has been beautifully maintained! When you enter the home, there is a HOME OFFICE to the right with built-in shelving. The layout of the home is spacious with a separate dining room, a living room, a laundry room, a kitchen with a separate eating area, and even a screened-in porch for all of the BBQs and family gatherings this summer! The 3 large bedrooms have spacious closets, and the 2 bathrooms both have DOUBLE SINKS! This home is not far from Universal Studios, SeaWorld, and all of the water parks and theme parks. In addition, the community of Arden Park offers so much to the residents including gated security measures, an Olympic-sized swimming pool, a beautiful clubhouse, a fitness center, a playground, a Tot Lot, and running and bicycle trails throughout. You don't want to miss it! This is a MUST-SEE house in one of the most beautiful communities so close to Orlando. Schedule your walk-through today!  copy link for walk-thru video   https://youtu.be/ldSuEUTa10M?si=inr8CfLj4rXDBj6T
